job seeking because Houston runs on energy. And so I was trying to make a change. And me and my

00:22:20.319 --> 00:22:23.920
one of my friends at the gym were like just chit-chatting about like what we were looking to

00:22:23.920 --> 00:22:30.400
do next. And my friend's wife happened to overhear that. And she said, oh, like you're like a nerd who

