yeah, it just I guess like to your point, Libby, it's we were like chit-chatting about like,

00:22:48.000 --> 00:22:53.920
I don't know, the very niche areas where we wanted to do our career pivots. And just someone

00:22:53.920 --> 00:22:58.959
happened to overhear that and say like, hey, I've got an opening that like fits that specific thing

00:22:58.959 --> 00:23:05.839
you're looking for. Yeah, it may be kind of old school, something I would actually if you're

