looking here in the job seeking, make business cards for yourself that are independent of your

00:23:10.800 --> 00:23:15.520
company. And they're cheap. You can get 250 business cards for less than 30 bucks. I just

00:23:15.520 --> 00:23:19.760
did that off Steepo and be like, you know, here's my name. Here's the thing I'm looking for.

00:23:21.040 --> 00:23:24.160
