00:27:30.880 --> 00:27:35.839
of any kind, whether it be consulting or if you're running a restaurant or whatever. And so,

00:27:35.839 --> 00:27:42.239
there's a lot of really great business books out there. And so, if you are wanting to start your

00:27:42.239 --> 00:27:51.520
own company, there's two books I'd recommend. One is called The E-Myth Revisited. And unfortunately,

00:27:51.520 --> 00:27:57.280
I did not write the author down on my notes beforehand. But it's basically saying when you

00:27:57.280 --> 00:28:03.119
